OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780600263
OL,3,CHospital Trust declares critical
OL,4,Cincident at two of it's hospitals
OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fby the NHS Trust in charge of
OL,8,FBasingstoke and Winchester hospitals.
OL,10,FHampshire Hospitals NHS Foundation
OL,11,FTrust announced its decision on
OL,12,FWednesday.
OL,14,FIt's blamed "extremely high" numbers
OL,15,Fof people attending its emergency
OL,16,Fdepartment, as well as a high
OL,17,Fadmission and low discharge rate.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
