FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780600263
OL,3,CHospital Trust declares critical
OL,4,Cincident at two of it's hospitals
OL,6,FThe Trust said these factors have had
OL,7,Fa "major impact on patient flow,
OL,8,Flimiting capacity and ability to admit
OL,9,Ffurther patients needing our care".
OL,11,FPeople are being asked to only attend
OL,12,Femergency department's in either
OL,13,FBasingstoke or Winchester in the event
OL,14,Fof an emergency.
OL,16,F"If you need medical assistance,
OL,17,Fplease use NHS111 who can direct you
OL,18,Fto the best alternative services such
OL,19,Fas your GP, pharmacy, or urgent
OL,20,Ftreatment centre," the trust said in a
OL,21,Fstatement.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
