OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780600263
OL,3,CHospital Trust declares critical
OL,4,Cincident at two of it's hospitals
OL,6,FAnyone with a pre-arranged procedure
OL,7,For appointment is being asked to
OL,8,Fattend as planned, unless you hear
OL,9,Fdirectly from the trust.
OL,11,FDr Nick Ward, deputy chief medical
OL,12,Fofficer for Hampshire Hospitals, says:
OL,13,F"Declaring a critical incident in
OL,14,Fearly summer is extremely unusual;
OL,15,Fhowever, it reflects the unprecedented
OL,16,Fattendance at our Emergency
OL,17,FDepartments as well as a high number
OL,18,Fof inpatients."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
