OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780600263
OL,3,CHospital Trust declares critical
OL,4,Cincident at two of it's hospitals
OL,6,FThe statement from the Trust said
OL,7,F"everything is being done increase
OL,8,Fcapacity for urgent emergency care in
OL,9,Four hospitals", adding "we appreciate
OL,10,Fthe public's support and patience
OL,11,Fduring this time".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
